{"tid":20683,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"教畜之路，我答你問！","createTime":"2016-12-03T13:17:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-16T02:57:42.000Z","uid":51704,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c6c24b92a33c348468b0ae2348c04302a10f6e39","tid":20683,"uid":51704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T13:17:48.000Z","msg":"由TA到0.5再到1。"},{"pid":"3487804c7c639039253420afb74d2ce1a68350be","tid":20683,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T13:47:56.000Z","msg":"而家做TA同新入職GM係咪好撚閪"},{"pid":"58754fc1f989c8c0162afcddc491336a3b6d5138","tid":20683,"uid":33983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T13:48:28.000Z","msg":"教咩科"},{"pid":"5fdc8980165ab951c3157004b24d868d80a8625f","tid":20683,"uid":51704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T15:16:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家做TA同新入職GM係咪好撚閪</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nTA =打雜：代課、影印、巡邏....校務處d人都可以吩咐你做嘢；階級觀念好重，TA自成一角。<br />\n我呢間新入職都係CM，校長講到明唔會輕易俾GM，你唔鍾意可以隨時走。仲有中學而家每年要cut 2個位，校長就日鳩日大你，大玩心理戰，perm嗰d 老屎忽話知你，最慘係d contract位，舊年先cut走咗一個做咗6、7年既contract位，條友無後台，無計。"},{"pid":"51c27475ce54d2875ca11a0c7150f40d4910405f","tid":20683,"uid":51704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T15:16:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>教咩科</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n某band 3中學 LS、地理、歷史"},{"pid":"c108073f0659ba5710ea25b40430366c2ca76e6d","tid":20683,"uid":23423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T15:19:50.000Z","msg":"行家"},{"pid":"b48f7d81d1a87d8d2e627dcb67f5d23f9db28c70","tid":20683,"uid":51704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T15:27:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>行家</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nching 都係咁樣？"},{"pid":"3a60098c45bdd10a6f75f342aadaf589e7f4c691","tid":20683,"uid":6964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T15:31:14.000Z","msg":"TA 升0.5 你會唔會唔慣"},{"pid":"54b7b8c22dec6cb43664df814e10e5b6c73405f1","tid":20683,"uid":23423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T15:34:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>行家</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nching 都係咁樣？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n直GM"},{"pid":"3d7357234227132faba09a5df7feb4d61c3bbe34","tid":20683,"uid":41803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T15:37:09.000Z","msg":"而家仲有冇人名為ta ， 人工ta, 但實際上要教書同做班主任？"},{"pid":"5166ec7289a48a8d70bf9c3c7e7d47f82097e9d9","tid":20683,"uid":51704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T15:37:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>TA 升0.5 你會唔會唔慣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n少少，不過做嘢其實差唔多，係有得教下書，10幾堂，唔駛成日影印，同埋校務處d人對你客氣d囉。不過都係同返d ta同事圍埋。呢行階級觀念太重。ta年年換人，好難有熟絡同事。"},{"pid":"a0b8f89a6869ebe054a914dd88daa24cbefb7b02","tid":20683,"uid":51704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T15:37:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>行家</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nching 都係咁樣？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n直GM</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁你都好好。未perm？"},{"pid":"7e63d999e604e3c7b52dfdd30fb964545d5cfac4","tid":20683,"uid":51704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T15:40:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家仲有冇人名為ta ， 人工ta, 但實際上要教書同做班主任？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大把。有同學就係咁。ta做班主任，上10堂，𢭃ta 13k人工。條友唔想咁快放棄，繼續捱落去，不過前景不明朗。"},{"pid":"e13e4d64cc5b88f95936aa21be250bd5fc00d276","tid":20683,"uid":45188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T16:02:46.000Z","msg":"同行，TA左3年，宜家1，果種轉變，有啲難適應<br />\n以前唔洗教書，只係跟NET上英文堂<br />\n利申：教小學"},{"pid":"4991229138b61bb8220cdfb6b77536c9ce3d849c","tid":20683,"uid":6964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T16:34:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>TA 升0.5 你會唔會唔慣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n少少，不過做嘢其實差唔多，係有得教下書，10幾堂，唔駛成日影印，同埋校務處d人對你客氣d囉。不過都係同返d ta同事圍埋。呢行階級觀念太重。ta年年換人，好難有熟絡同事。</blockquote><br />\n你係個間中學GRAD?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf85b976654261356a60b75716076d30f34724ad","tid":20683,"uid":33983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T16:35:48.000Z","msg":"想入行教bafs點睇"},{"pid":"15c4acb3edb0ae49730fac16c53253dd15cfc2d2","tid":20683,"uid":51704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T16:43:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>TA 升0.5 你會唔會唔慣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n少少，不過做嘢其實差唔多，係有得教下書，10幾堂，唔駛成日影印，同埋校務處d人對你客氣d囉。不過都係同返d ta同事圍埋。呢行階級觀念太重。ta年年換人，好難有熟絡同事。</blockquote><br />\n你係個間中學GRAD?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係啊<br />\n做緊第3年<br />\n都有幾個舊生係度做緊1"},{"pid":"e1f9c37e37fa31f6c9dd8116bee189d3b22b5500","tid":20683,"uid":51704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T16:45:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想入行教bafs點睇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n要識教多幾科好喔<br />\nbafs選修科cover太大<br />\n一般水平學生都跟得頗辛苦。<br />\n讀完又好似半桶水。<br />\n搵band3就易d，流失率高"},{"pid":"656fe4c8ec39ddb409f0b1c0587097c37a304e34","tid":20683,"uid":23902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T16:50:31.000Z","msg":"見到你教band3 以為識你<br />\n點知教geog<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69119926caaeaedf8382152ff283589a43758deb","tid":20683,"uid":51704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T16:53:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見到你教band3 以為識你<br />\n點知教geog<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你教ls hist？"},{"pid":"01608f4c3a4700e39b0ccd68decef46349bf0047","tid":20683,"uid":33983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T04:20:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想入行教bafs點睇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n要識教多幾科好喔<br />\nbafs選修科cover太大<br />\n一般水平學生都跟得頗辛苦。<br />\n讀完又好似半桶水。<br />\n搵band3就易d，流失率高</blockquote><br />\n但如果淨係讀bafs既pgde, 可唔可以教埋econ"},{"pid":"575a0edf50888482c0cc59aba26e888464ccd8b9","tid":20683,"uid":51704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T14:58:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想入行教bafs點睇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n要識教多幾科好喔<br />\nbafs選修科cover太大<br />\n一般水平學生都跟得頗辛苦。<br />\n讀完又好似半桶水。<br />\n搵band3就易d，流失率高</blockquote><br />\n但如果淨係讀bafs既pgde, 可唔可以教埋econ</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你first degree 係乜？<br />\n我呢間校長好重視first degree，要對到科<br />\n例如高中地理都係搵返本科係地理既人<br />\n高中大路科都係專科專教，再兼教其他<br />\necon老師本科都係econ<br />\nbafs就係會計<br />\npgde其實都係bonus<br />\n有同學係請咗先至後補，或者讀咗一半已經有人請"},{"pid":"47df3b4d54e76cb0ac480399903a73fa54b0f2c1","tid":20683,"uid":49508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T11:12:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>行家</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nching 都係咁樣？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n直GM</blockquote><br />\n直GM +1 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fefa0354b7f01dfa4db0db186c5703dbf32412f9","tid":20683,"uid":28960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T15:56:39.000Z","msg":"想問下degree讀啲唔關事既野<br />\n想教chem既話係咪讀返pdge就夠<br />\n會唔會無人請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e121f29d44e010430a5636994828e722252d9e23","tid":20683,"uid":35303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T16:04:01.000Z","msg":"中學music留名<br />\n利申岸已上<br />\n有得留就留左先啦<br />\n18年又打到來<br />\n出面又風大雨大返"}]}